    {
      "name": "Emergency Carrier (Converted)",
      "desc": "Cargo hauler converted to a makeshift carrier because the fleet lost too many real ones. Her flight deck is a cargo bay with the doors welded open, her catapult is a repurposed ore launcher, and her pilots land on a deck that was never designed for the purpose. She loses a fighter to landing accidents every week. She's also the reason the fleet still has air cover, so nobody complains.",
      "notes": "Improvised carrier. 20-30 fighters. High accident rate. Desperate times.",
      "size": 18,
      "loco": "space_ftl",
      "toughLevel": 0,
      "armourLevel": 0,
      "speedLevel": -1,
